## Provider Contracts

These providers have established consumer contracts. Changing their API is a breaking change.

| Provider | Required companion | Consumer usage |
|----------|-------------------|----------------|
| `ToastProvider` | `Toaster` (from sonner) | Apps render `<Toaster />` alongside |
| `LocaleProvider` | `changeLocale` export | Apps call `changeLocale()` for language switch |
| `OverlayProvider` | `overlayStore` export | Apps pass store instance |
| `createTabProvider(...)` | factory function | Apps create per-package tab providers |

### Rules

1. Do not remove or rename exported provider props without semver-major intent.
2. `toast` should be imported from `sonner` directly, not re-exported from this package.
3. When adding optional props to a provider, ensure existing consumers work without the new prop.
4. Document new required companions in the relevant barrel or `AI_GUIDE.md`.
